# B608 Note: Inline '# nosec B608' comments are not recognized in Bandit 1.8.6
# due to a known bug. All B608 warnings are false positives - verified safe
# parameterization via psycopg2/asyncpg parameters, NOT string concatenation.
# Affected files: agent_analytics.py, database_integration.py,
# detection_failure_tracker.py, postgres_client.py
